  <title>Downtown Minneapolis</title>

  <title>Summer Vignette</title>
  <link>http://porkchopposterous.wordpress.com/2010/07/25/summer-vignette/</link>
  <pubDate>Sun, 25 Jul 2010 00:04:27 +0000</pubDate>

  <title>Spooky is the deafest kitty I know</title>
  <link>http://porkchopposterous.wordpress.com/2010/08/01/spooky-is-the-deafest-kitty-i-know/</link>

  <title>Just another snowpocalypse</title>
  <link>http://porkchopposterous.wordpress.com/2011/03/23/just-another-snowpocalypse/</link>
  <pubDate>Wed, 23 Mar 2011 21:29:12 +0000</pubDate>

<item>
  <title>Nikki just refilled my wine glass</title>
  <link>http://porkchopposterous.wordpress.com/2011/04/02/nikki-just-refilled-my-wine-glass/</link>
  <pubDate>Sat, 02 Apr 2011 02:04:40 +0000</pubDate>

  <title>Ellipses keeps it classy</title>
  <link>http://porkchopposterous.wordpress.com/2011/08/03/ellipses-keeps-it-classy/</link>

<item>
  <title>We belong to the light, we belong to the thunder...</title>
  <link>http://porkchopposterous.wordpress.com/2011/09/16/we-belong-to-the-light-we-belong-to-the-thund/</link>
  <pubDate>Fri, 16 Sep 2011 02:25:51 +0000</pubDate>
  <dc:creator>aeberg</dc:creator>

  <title>Mini Mascot! Adorable</title>

  <title>This mess created with assistance from my blow-dryer</title>

  <title>... And I made a sweet treat to share with my sweetie when he gets home.</title>
